{
  "macro_id": "masonry.wallStrength",
  "domain": "masonry",
  "name": "wallStrength",
  "inputs": {
    "heightFeet": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "thicknessInches": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "reinforced": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "loadBearing": {
      "type": "boolean"
    }
  },
  "reads_artifact_data": true,
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.slendernessRatio === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.maxAllowedRatio === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.passesSlenderness === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.recommendation === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.slendernessRatio)",
    "output.ok === false || (output.result.reinforced ? output.result.maxAllowedRatio === 25 : output.result.maxAllowedRatio === 20)"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "heightFeet": 8,
            "thicknessInches": 8,
            "reinforced": true
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "heightFeet": 30,
            "thicknessInches": 6,
            "reinforced": false
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {}
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "heightFeet": "Infinity",
            "thicknessInches": 0
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": false
      }
    }
  ],
  "_note": "Pure compute, reads artifact.data (MasonStuff channel). slendernessRatio = (heightFeet × 12) / thicknessInches, rounded to 0.1; maxAllowedRatio = 25 (reinforced) / 20 (unreinforced); passesSlenderness = ratio ≤ max; recommendation grades adequate / near-limit (>80% of max) / too-slender. Non-finite or non-positive height/thickness fall to defaults 8/8 (Number.isFinite guard) — slenderness is never NaN/Infinity. Result card renders heightFeet/thicknessInches/slendernessRatio/maxAllowedRatio/passesSlenderness/reinforced/loadBearing/recommendation EXACTLY."
}
